data.description: THIS LOVELY 4/2/2 HOME IS LOCATED IN THE DESIRABLE, WELL ESTABLISHED SUBDIVISION OF DOWLEN WEST. IT INCLUDES A FORMAL DINING ROOM, FORMAL LIVING ROOM, BREAKFAST NOOK, AS WELL AS A STAIRWAY/BALCONY OVERLOOKING A DEN WITH A WOOD BURNING FIREPLACE. THE PRIMARY BEDROOM WITH HIS AND HERS CLOSETS IS LOCATED ON THE FIRST FLOOR WHILE THE REMAINING 3 VERY SPACIOUS BEDROOMS ARE UPSTAIRS. ALSO ENJOY THE SUNROOM, BACKYARD WITH PRIVACY FENCE AND ADDITIONAL CLIMATE CONTROLLED STORAGE LOCATED RIGHT OFF THE GARAGE- POSSIBLY YOUR OFFICE SPACE!
